== 飛行事故 ==
由於F-4涉及的飛行事故太多，下文只列出最重大的事故。

* 1971年6月6日，美國[[休斯西部航空706號班機空難|休斯西部航空706號班機]]（[[DC-9|DC-9-31]]）在執行[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]國際機場到[[鹽湖城|鹽湖城]]的飛行中，與一架F-4B在[[聖蓋博山|聖蓋博山]]上空相撞，客機上所有49名乘員和F-4上的一名空勤人員遇難<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,905174,00.html |title=The Nation: Fatal Sequence |accessdate=2009-12-10 |work= |publisher=TIME |date=Jun 21, 1971 |archive-date=2009-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090928220320/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,905174,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

* 1974年8月9日，一架英國皇家空軍的鬼怪FGR2和一家民用的PA-25「承典人」農用撒種飛機在英國諾福克上空相撞，兩機上的三名乘員全部遇難<ref name="aaib">{{cite web |author= |title=Report No:9/1975 Piper PA25-235, G-ASVX and Phantom FGR2, XV493. Report on the collison at Fordham Fen, Norfolk, on 9 August 1974 |url=http://www.aaib.gov.uk/cms_resources.cfm?file=/9-1975%20G-ASVX%20and%20XV493.pdf |work= |publisher=[[Air_Accidents_Investigation_Branch|Air Accidents Investigation Branch]] |date=20 June 1975 |accessdate=28 September 2009 |archive-date=2012-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120601205816/http://www.aaib.gov.uk/cms_resources.cfm?file=%2F9-1975%20G-ASVX%20and%20XV493.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="Flight1154">{{cite journal | last =  | first =  | title = Collision over Norfolk | journal = [[Flight_International|Flight International]] | pages = 146 | date = 15 August 1974 | url = http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1974/1974%20-%201154.html | access-date = 2009-12-10 | archive-date = 2012-10-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021040224/http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1974/1974%20-%201154.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

